'''Azureus Vuze''' (formerly Azureus) is a [[BitTorrent client]]. Like other BitTorrent clients, it is used to transfer files via the [[BitTorrent (protocol)|BitTorrent]] protocol, a mechanism for [[peer-to-peer]] [[file sharing]] over a network. Azureus is written in [[Java (programming language)|Java]] [[programming language]] .
